╭──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮
│Get details about a specific ability.                                     │
│                                                                          │
│ USAGE:                                                                   │
│    poke-cli ability <ability-name>                                       │
│    Use a hyphen when typing a name with a space.                         │
│                                                                          │
│ FLAGS:                                                                   │
│    -h, --help                     Prints the help menu.                  │
│    -p, --pokemon                  Prints Pokémon that learn this ability.│
╰──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯